{"type": "article", "id": 5417, "title": "儿童用体温贴 eSkin Thermometer", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-21T07:27:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233851L3hqkRjFdxJ8PDSa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t位于硅谷的 Vivalnk 公司在今年的 CES 展上推出一款儿童用体温贴 eSkin Thermometer 。设计团队赋予其小熊图案，可爱的泰迪熊当然是为了讨儿童的欢心。这款儿童用体温贴最核心的功能还是测量体表温度，只要将它贴在皮肤上三秒，再用手机经 NFC 触碰就可以知道体温时多少了。VivaLnk 公司表示,这款泰迪熊体温贴是可以清洗的，在开封后可以使用 15 天左右。<a href=\"http://www.vivalnk.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这款体温贴将于今年春天上市</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233849D9sLBqkEQuS6JNhy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233849JAcdGHqtTYZrmvI1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233850gNlD4fVIuO9z57Be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233850n7cO3btXUvsPFS8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}